text: Calbe (Saale) Stadt station is a railway station in the northern part of the municipality of Calbe (Saale), located in the Salzlandkreis district in Saxony-Anhalt, Germany. ==References== ==External links== Category:Railway stations in Saxony-Anhalt Category:Buildings and structures in Salzlandkreis Category:Railway stations in Germany opened in 2014
title: Calbe (Saale) Stadt station
